	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Donkey Kong Land 2 timing [solved]</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />BGB confirms inaccessible VRAM writes and the game functions normally even when these writes are blocked.  It's strange, but it functions.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
